data.description: Beautifully appointed 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with over 1,900 Sq Ft of living space. The home has an open concept floor plan with the kitchen, living and breakfast nook. Separate bonus media room or formal dining room located just off the entry doorway on the front side of the home. Vinyl plank flooring throughout the main living areas with carpet in the bedrooms and ceramic tile in the bathrooms. The kitchen offers granite counters, shaker cabinets, stainless appliances and a center island.  Featuring a split bedroom plan, the expansive master bedroom is on the back side of the home with views of back yard. Large master bathroom with double vanities, separate shower, and huge walk-in closet. The home is located in The Villages of Mill Bayou, next to North Bay Haven Charter Academy, featuring a beautiful community pool, picnic area, fire pit, and pavilion/gazebo.
